  "description": "Otrium FX chain demo — 3 atmosphere engines breathe in a slow equilateral triangle, sync-locked to host tempo (1 cycle per beat). Long attack/release ducks softly; partner-driven coupling depth blends autonomous LFO with each engine's envelope. Hold a chord and the pad rotates around itself indefinitely. Otrium config embedded under Obsidian's parameter block; engines load into slots 0/1/2 in order.",
